{"tid":1295323,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"點解入香港警察？","createTime":"2019-07-08T03:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T04:04:06.000Z","uid":57695,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f86050601c2f2af5b64a5c84ccc9f543f0acec06","tid":1295323,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:45:19.000Z","msg":"點解入香港警察？<br />\n巴閉囉，英雄主義，疊馬。<br />\n我唔妥你，我可以𢭃你；<br />\n我唔鍾意你，我可以塔你。<br />\n𡃁仔你睥咩呀？出嚟隻揪吖！<br />\n隻揪呀！頂撚住我呀！<br />\n揪我吖！揪吖！<br />\n我揪你你揪我，點呀？<br />\n你見過暴動未呀？你見過死全家未呀？<br />\n你話梁天琦你偶像吖嘛，你見過梁天琦未呀？<br />\n勇武派揸fit人吖嘛，好巴閉呀？<br />\n你知唔知佢手足畀人告暴動佢掹唔到；<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住佢手足，坐，流亡，佢救唔到。<br />\n你知唔知梁天琦諗緊咩呀？<br />\n話畀你聽佢唔想做揸fit人，<br />\n佢唔想入獄，<br />\n但係佢冇辦法，冇得返轉頭。<br />\n係呀，每個人都有偶像，我都有。<br />\n其實，讀唔讀書，我讀唔到咁多，<br />\n但係我想話畀你聽，讀毅進，冇得返轉頭。"},{"pid":"8346c598c2ce3c3d308b5454601f981578e7344c","tid":1295323,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:46:22.000Z","msg":"打人唔洗證已經要仆入去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78406ae00bfde89589f70d6e747c49bd197e96c4","tid":1295323,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"啱啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191fc97ec91af46ea04ac5a059ad9d18f9e46458","tid":1295323,"uid":50658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 你呢段本身設定係比陳浩南講番陳浩南做偶像<br />\n有待改進"},{"pid":"6f7146efeeb17789c3a40c8c975fa0f88ae56eec","tid":1295323,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YeHRZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YeHRZu.jpg&h=96834243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<